        <h2 class="name2">----FLOAT LIKE A BUTTERFLY STING LIKE A BEE----</h2>

        <p class ="para">Muhammad Ali (1942-2016) was an American former heavyweight champion boxer and
             one of the greatest sporting figures of the 20th century. An Olympic gold medalist and the 
             first fighter to capture the heavyweight title three times, Ali won 56 times in his 21-year professional career.
              "The Greatest", he is widely regarded as one of the most significant and celebrated sports figures of the 20th century, 
              and is frequently ranked as the greatest heavyweight boxer of all time.
        </p>

